data.description: Welcome to this move-in ready home with brand new carpet and a freshly painted interior. As you step inside, you'll notice the beautiful laminate wood flooring and the 9ft ceilings that creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom complete with a double vanity, shower & garden tub. Situated on a private wooded lot, this home offers a serene and peaceful setting. This home has the added bonus of being just steps away from a walking trail. This trail leads to a community park and pool, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation.
